    readxl,
    Seurat,
    RColorBrewer,
    ggplot2,
    cowplot,
    tidyverse,
    matrixStats,
    viridis,
    stats,
    dplyr,
    effsize,
    rlang
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
